      "message": "See answer above - this var and others removed from this file.\nA1_ADAPTER/A1_CONTROLLER is more an indication of the current target functionality for this test environment. \nHowever, it would be better with a generic name as it could be confusing if additional functionality will be tested. Will consider renaming when refactoring the test environment.",
